Other works
Movie career
Chou formally entered the film industry in 2005 with the release of the movie Initial D film Initial D . He has since acted in three other movies, directed one film and more than a dozen music videos. Chou, who once said I live because of music,zh icon cite book   last = Chou    first = Jay    title = Grandeur de D Major   publisher = Hua Ren Ban Tu    date = 2004    pages = p.109    month = December    isbn = 957-29371-4-6   ventured into movies because he felt the need for a new challenge. As fans have grown concerned that movies will compromise his music career, Chou has repeatedly reassured that movies are a source of inspiration and not a distraction; at the same time, he realizes the need to balance both careers and maintain his place in the music field to garner the continued support of fans.zh icon cite web  url = http://ol.mingpao.com/cfm/star5.cfm?File=20070107/saa01/mak1.txt   title = Jay Chou on the directors road   date = 2007-01-07   accessdate = 2007-06-02   publisher = Mingpao   format = Interview zh icon cite news  url = http://music.yule.sohu.com/20070329/n249054788.shtml   title = Plans to slowly distance from movies and other occupations/ Jay Chou will return to music     date = 2007-03-29   accessdate = 2007-06-02   publisher = /Sohu   format = News article zh icon cite news  url = http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/6/4/10/n1282561.htm   title = Jay Chou: the joy in filming cannot be found in music anymore :   date = 2006-04-10   accessdate = 2007-06-02   publisher = Epoch Times   format = News article zh icon cite web  url = http://ent.tom.com/2006-12-14/0016/32559464.html   title = The invincible Jay Chou: its good to be number one    date = 2006-12-14   accessdate = 2007-06-02   publisher = ent.tom.com   format = Interview 
=Acting=
