Notes
a.note_label A a none Examples of Chou's Zhong guo feng R&B: East Wind Breaks , Hair Like Snow , Faraway . Examples of Zhong guo feng rock: Nunchucks , Dragon Fist , Golden Armor .
b.note_label B b none Examples of sound effects used in Chou's music: ping pong balls in Third Year Second Class , touch-tone phone dialing in Blue Storm , helicopter blades in My Territory , dripping rain in You Can Hear , and radio static noise in Nocturne .
c.note_label C c none Examples of Oriental-style lyrics by Vincent Fang: Shanghai 1943 , Wife , and Chrysanthemum Flower Platform .
d.note_label D d none Examples of romantic lyrics by Vincent Fang: Love Before Anno Domini , Nocturne , Common Jasmine Orange , and Perfectionist  .
e.note_label E e none Vincent Fang's lyrics discuss war in The Last Battle  and Wounds That End War , the Bible in Blue Storm , sports in Bullfight  and Third Year Second Class , and martial arts in Nunchucks  and Ninja .
f.note_label F f none Examples of Vivian Hsu's work: Adorable Woman , Tornado , and Simple Love .
g.note_label G g none Unusual themes of Huan Jun Lang's lyrics: detective story in Twilight's Chapter Seven , a chess game in Checkmate .
h.note_label H h none Examples of romantic lyrics by Jay Chou: Black Humor , Silence , Iron Box Of An Island , Fine Day , Excuse , Black Sweater , and White Windmills .
i.note_label I i none Snail  and Listen To Your Mother 
j.note_label J j none Golden Melody Awards: the Chinese pop music industry's equivalent of the Grammy Awards in the US are held annually to award professionals making music in Mandarin, Taiwanese, Hakka and any of Taiwan's Aboriginal languages.cite news  last = Woodworth   first = Max  url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/feat/archives/2005/05/29/2003257129  title=The red carpet rolls out for Golden Melody Awards  publisher=Taipei Times  date=2005-05-29   accessdate = 2007-06-02 
k.note_label K k none A similar book was published in Japanese, titled Grandeur de D majorJay Chou Photo Essay ISBN 4901873504.
